string_data: This black and white photograph shows five men standing together on a dock at London Docks, posing in front of a large vessel named "Gondwana." The ship appears to be a substantial maritime vessel with multiple decks, rigging, and communication equipment. The men are dressed casually in jackets and sweaters, with one wearing what appears to be a Greenpeace-related t-shirt. The dock setting and industrial background are clearly visible.
